high_descs: Walk straight ahead to the sink on your right.
Remove the egg under the faucet, in the sink.
Turn to the microwave, above the stove to your left.
Place the egg in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the egg from the microwave.
Turn around and walk between the sink and the kitchen island, past the refrigerator, to the garbage can on the floor, to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the egg in the garbage can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm egg in the garbage can.

high_descs: Walk forward and then turn right to face the sink on the right.
Pick up an egg that's behind the drain from the sink.
Turn and walk to the stove, look above the stove at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the egg inside the microwave, close the door, heat the egg, open the door, take the egg out, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the black bin on the floor to the right of the fridge.
Place the egg inside of the black bin.
anns.task_desc: To heat an egg and place it inside the black bin.

high_descs: Go forward to the sink that is on the right.
Pick up the egg that is under the faucet in the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the microwave that is above the stove.
Put the egg inside the microwave and turn it on, remove the cooked egg from the microwave.
Turn to the right, go to the counter, hang a right, go to the wall, turn left, go to the garbage can.
Put the egg in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the garbage can.
